### Get User by ID (UUID)
POST {{cms_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query GetUserById($id: UUID!) { userById(id: $id) { id version name email isActive createdAt updatedAt deletedAt isDeleted } }",
  "variables": {
    "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
  }
}

